summary: BELLEVUE, Wash., November 20, 2024--It’s the haul-iday season and T-Mobile (NASDAQ: TMUS) and Metro by T-Mobile are celebrating with serious savings on the latest tech — including great deals for business customers, too. Right now, T-Mobile customers can score the latest iPhone 16 lineup, built for Apple Intelligence, on Us.
